# Privacy Policy for Word Scramble Master 50

**Effective Date:** [25-04-2026]

**Word Scramble Master 50** ("the App," "we," "us," or "our") provides a free-to-play, offline mobile gaming experience. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding any information collected when you use our App. 

By using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

---

### 1. Data Collection and Usage
Word Scramble Master 50 is designed to respect your privacy. Because the App is built primarily as an **offline** game:

* **No Personal Information Collected:** We do not explicitly require, collect, or store any personally identifiable information (such as your name, email address, phone number, or physical address) to play the game.
* **No Account Required:** You do not need to create an account or log in to play.
* **Offline Play:** The core gameplay does not require an active internet connection, meaning your game progress and settings are saved locally directly on your device.

### 2. Third-Party Services
While we do not collect personal data directly, the App is built using the Unity Engine and may contain third-party services that collect data to provide core functionality, analytics, or advertisements.

* **Unity Engine:** The game is built using Unity. Unity may automatically collect device information (such as IP address, device type, and operating system) to ensure the game runs smoothly. You can review Unity’s privacy policy here: [Unity Privacy Policy](https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy)
* **Advertising Networks (If Applicable):** To keep the game 100% free, we may partner with third-party advertising networks (such as Google AdMob or Unity Ads). These networks may use temporary cookies or mobile advertising identifiers (such as the Android Advertising ID) to serve personalized or non-personalized ads. 

### 3. Permissions Requested
The App may request the following standard device permissions to function correctly:
* **Storage/Media:** To save and load your game progress locally on your device.
* **Network Access:** Required only if the App needs to serve advertisements or report crash logs. As stated, the game itself is playable offline.

### 4. Children’s Privacy
Word Scramble Master 50 is a family-friendly game suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information through a third-party service, please contact us so we can take necessary actions.

### 5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon publishing the updated policy on this page or within the App store listing. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

